descriptor.name: APRICOT
descriptor.short_desc: Apricots (Prunus armeniaca) are stone fruits also known as Armenian plums. Round and yellow, they look like a smaller version of a peach but share the tartness of purple plums. They're extremely nutritious and have many health benefits, such as improved digestion and eye health.
